"  Miso sambal:","2 tablespoons chile paste with garlic (such as Sambal oelek)","2 tablespoons chopped peeled fresh ginger","2 tablespoons white miso (soybean paste)","2 tablespoons rice wine vinegar","1 1/2 tablespoons sugar","1 1/2 teaspoons dark sesame oil","  Wraps:","1 cup matchstick-cut English cucumber","1/2 cup cilantro sprigs","2 tablespoons chopped dry-roasted peanuts","1  (12.3-ounce) package reduced-fat firm tofu, drained and cut into 1/2-inch-thick strips","1/2  avocado, peeled and thinly sliced","12  large Boston lettuce leaves"